title: War of the Roses: Her Friend Saw Him on Tinder
description: Stacy's friend saw Stacy's boyfriend Todd on Tinder.  Her friend sent her screenshots of Todd's profile but when Stacy confronted him, Todd said that someone must be using his pictures and that it's a fake account.   Is it really fake or is Todd on Tinder being sketchy?
